@startuml
!pragma layout smetana

left to right direction
hide circle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam defaultFontName Consolas

title File Service Data Model (No Relational DB)

entity "stored_files\n(logical object, not SQL table)" as stored_files {
  *file_name : uuid.ext
  --
  content : binary
  storage_backend : local fs | gcs
  original_extension : derived
}

entity "temporary_links\n(ephemeral response model)" as temporary_links {
  *file_name : uuid.ext
  --
  url : text
  expires_at_utc : timestamptz
}

stored_files ||--o{ temporary_links

note bottom of stored_files
Actual persistence:
- local filesystem (/app/uploads), or
- Google Cloud Storage bucket

The service does not keep relational metadata.
This diagram is a logical storage model only.
end note

@enduml
